Your `NoteList` message type contains a single field `notes` that is a list of `Note` messages. To send a message of that type you need to send an object with a single field that is a list of `Note`-like objects. In this case, that should look like this:

```js
const notes = { notes: [
    { id: &#39;1&#39;, title: &#39;Note 1&#39;, content: &#39;Content 1&#39;},
    { id: &#39;2&#39;, title: &#39;Note 2&#39;, content: &#39;Content 2&#39;}
  ]
}
```

